 to become obsessed of live football shows to get yourself updated with what is happening with your favorite team. When you cannot go the location where a football game is happening, the field of technology was able to find the best option for you to keep yourself updated all the time. The technological advancements made in technology was very effective in producing live football streams for people to subscribe. The internet is actually one of the many breakthroughs in the field of technology that can help you in so many ways. With the help of technology, people can now use the internet to look for live football videos that you would want to watch. The internet is actually very useful for people if they had been anticipating to witness a football match they had been waiting for all the time live. Because of the internet, people can now check for websites that offer football live streaming videos according to their needs.<br />\n<a href="http://sportsstreamingguide.webnode.com/page-2/">Learning The Secrets About Options</a><br />\n Football live streams can actually work if you know the things that you must learn about these types of websites. People will have the chance to enjoy the perks of football live streams if networking is involved. There is a need for you to know that in networking information for live football stream, you will have to deal with data exchanges from two existing computers.<br />\n<a href="https://livefootballshows.joomla.com/2-uncategorised/4-how-to-stream-your-favorite-nfl-games">Services Tips for The Average Joe</a><br />\n For live football video streams to be successful, streaming media should do something about it. Streaming media can actually help you find the best websites that you need to see the football match that your favorite team has. People can easily witness the things that live football matches can give to them in video stream with the use of streaming media server. If you want your streaming to become more efficient and satisfying, you will have to get yourself a very fast connection in the internet. You have to remember that there are so many benefits that you can get if you have a live football video stream with you. Nothing is perfect in this world that you should learn to embrace the drawbacks that may occur along the way. Knowing how live football streams can give you the entertainment that you need, you will realize how important these forms of media are.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:62:"http://wp4sae.org/5-takeaways-that-i-learned-about-sports/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:41:"Products – Getting Started & Next Steps";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"http://wp4sae.org/products-getting-started-next-steps";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:61:"http://wp4sae.org/products-getting-started-next-steps#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 13 Apr 2016 04:53:35 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:18:"Sports & Athletics";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"http://wp4sae.org/products-getting-started-next-steps";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:408:"What Are The Benefits That Athletes Can Get From Carrying A Sports Bottle? Being an athlete, it is always a requirement for everyone to carry with them sports water bottles so that they are being hydrated for the duration of their practices or tournaments. One of the things that can keep your body functioning is<a class="more-link" href="http://wp4sae.org/products-getting-started-next-steps">Read more</a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"writer";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2953:"<p><img src="http://www.clubrowcreations.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sports-water-bottles-120213-1024x1024.jpg" style="width:138px;float:right;margin:1em" />What Are The Benefits That Athletes Can Get From Carrying A Sports Bottle? Being an athlete, it is always a requirement for everyone to carry with them sports water bottles so that they are being hydrated for the duration of their practices or tournaments. One of the things that can keep your body functioning is by drinking water because it allows you to refill the amount of liquid that were gone from your body. If you are not participating in any sports tournament at the moment, it is still important for you to keep yourself hydrated by taking in sufficient amount of water in order for your performance to be maintained at the highest level it can be. Anyone can actually use sports bottles as they are not just for athletes to use alone. If it is within the scope of your interest to improve your health better, then drinking a lot of water and other beverages that are low in calories can actually ensure you that your body will become as healthy as it can be. Having water bottles can be convenient for you especially in keeping yourself hydrated while being able to carry it around as easy as you can. Determining the sport or the activity that you are going to participate with will certainly help you choose the best sport water bottle that you can use for your needs. If you are a cyclist, then the best type of water bottles for you are those who have nozzles or flip caps since there is no such need for you to use both of your hands. When you are drinking water from a bottle with nozzles, then you may find yourself in a dire situation since these bottles are a bit difficult to handle compared to those who have caps. When you plan to go to a gym for some work out sessions, there is no need for you to use water bottles with nozzles since you can freely use your hands and you also have time to open capped bottles. Plus the fact that drinking from capped bottles are much easier compared to those with nozzles. When you are doing some physical activities, it is important the you keep yourself hydrated so that your body can do its functions better and in order for this to remain, your way of drinking can determine the amount of fluid intakes enters your body. Once you come to terms with the water bottle style that you want to use then deciding to purchase one for yourself will be an easy thing to do. There are ways where in you can obtain the water bottle of your choice: you can either get it from the store in your area, buy one online, or obtain one from those promotional giveaways.<a href="http://bestwaterbottles.pen.io/">Getting Creative With Products Advice</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://sportswaterbottlesworld.tumblr.com/post/141877179656/the-benefits-of-using-reusable-sports-water">Interesting Research on Reviews &#8211; Things You Probably Never Knew</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:58:"http://wp4sae.org/products-getting-started-next-steps/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:47:"A Quick Overlook of Bottles – Your Cheatsheet";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:61:"http://wp4sae.org/a-quick-overlook-of-bottles-your-cheatsheet";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:69:"http://wp4sae.org/a-quick-overlook-of-bottles-your-cheatsheet#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 13 Apr 2016 04:52:40 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:18:"Sports & Athletics";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:61:"http://wp4sae.org/a-quick-overlook-of-bottles-your-cheatsheet";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:398:"Types Of Sports Water Bottles You Can Buy Are you an athlete and there happens to be competition for the following day, then there are quite a lot of things that you must prepare. Whether it is your safety gears, your shoes or anything, it is essential that you are concern on your safety before<a class="more-link" href="http://wp4sae.org/a-quick-overlook-of-bottles-your-cheatsheet">Read more</a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"writer";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2919:"<p><img src="http://g03.a.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1Du7THFXXXXX6aXXXq6xXFXXXS/-font-b-600ml-b-font-Stainless-Steel-font-b-Water-b-font-font-b-Bottle.jpg" style="width:129px;float:right;margin:1em" />Types Of Sports Water Bottles You Can Buy Are you an athlete and there happens to be competition for the following day, then there are quite a lot of things that you must prepare. Whether it is your safety gears, your shoes or anything, it is essential that you are concern on your safety before you go on competing. There are lots of people who say that you have to look for your team if you&#8217;re a part of one but just before that, you need to look for yourself first. There are so many things that they must remember like knowledge and better training to keep them focused in their goals. Not only that, keeping a healthy body also help them to find success in their career. The biggest enemies of athletes are dehydration which is why it is very important to always bring a bottle of water. Water is what needed no matter if you&#8217;re a regular individual or an athlete. In anything that a person do, this keeps them hydrated. On the other hand, there are numerous types of sports water bottle that fits to the kind of sports that you play. If an athlete wants to win, then they know they could not just settle for ordinary bottle of water.<br />\n<a href="http://sportswaterbottlesworld.tumblr.com/post/141877179656/the-benefits-of-using-reusable-sports-water">News For This Month: Water</a><br />\n There are many types of sports that we know today and each of it has a certain kind of water bottle. A cyclist uses a kind of bottle that suits perfectly to the compartment of their bikes. And because they are on the go always, they need to move fast and must use water bottle that can be easily opened. They can&#8217;t use those that need both hands to open as their hands are the ones they use in stirring their ride. To be able to squeeze the water and cap, cyclist needs a bottle with flexi-grip.<br />\n<a href="http://sportswaterbottle.yolasite.com/bestwaterbottles.php">The 10 Commandments of Reviews And How Learn More</a><br />\n Hikers are other athletes that need a special type of water bottle. Because canteen types of bottles are light in weight and easy to grip, they are quite popular for them. They can be handy and doesn&#8217;t take much space in the bags. And for athletes who are playing outside the court, they are not much concerned on the physical appearance of their water bottle. They&#8217;re just concerned on the condition of water after playing under the sun for long hours whether it is screw cap, a flexi-grip or what not. Such athletes want sports water bottle with insulation in order to keep their water cool. When you are an athlete, it may seem irrelevant to use water bottles but in reality, this plays an integral role to keep you functional and healthy throughout your game.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:66:"http://wp4sae.org/a-quick-overlook-of-bottles-your-cheatsheet/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34:"The perfect place for your parents";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:52:"http://wp4sae.org/the-perfect-place-for-your-parents";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"http://wp4sae.org/the-perfect-place-for-your-parents#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 12 Apr 2016 16:32:08 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16:"Health & Fitness";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:52:"http://wp4sae.org/the-perfect-place-for-your-parents";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:371:"In case you have old parents, I am sure that you are doing your best to keep them healthy and satisfied. However, you also have a job that requires you to spend time away from home, and that is not something that you can change, right? So, I suggest that you go to the official<a class="more-link" href="http://wp4sae.org/the-perfect-place-for-your-parents">Read more</a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"writer";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:602:"<p>In case you have old parents, I am sure that you are doing your best to keep them healthy and satisfied. However, you also have a job that requires you to spend time away from home, and that is not something that you can change, right? So, I suggest that you go to the official website of this center called Independent Living Systems. If you do that, you will see that there is a place where your parents can experience the best <a href="http://ilshealthservices.com">Florida health care support services for transition</a>. This center will make them feel appreciated and valued all the time.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"http://wp4sae.org/the-perfect-place-for-your-parents/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:39:"Why People Think Kayaks Are A Good Idea";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"http://wp4sae.org/why-people-think-kayaks-are-a-good-idea";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:65:"http://wp4sae.org/why-people-think-kayaks-are-a-good-idea#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 12 Apr 2016 14:41:01 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:18:"Sports & Athletics";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"http://wp4sae.org/why-people-think-kayaks-are-a-good-idea";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:410:"Benefits That Come With Renting A Kayak Paddling recreational kayak on a class 1 water requires no special training as anyone can almost do it. The one question that most interested individuals would like to know is whether they have to buy their own kayak or rent a kayak instead? The more ideal option between<a class="more-link" href="http://wp4sae.org/why-people-think-kayaks-are-a-good-idea">Read more</a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"writer";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2974:"<p><img src="http://i.istockimg.com/file_thumbview_approve/11347313/3/stock-photo-11347313-tandem-kayaks-for-rent.jpg" style="width:375px;float:right;margin:1em" />Benefits That Come With Renting A Kayak Paddling recreational kayak on a class 1 water requires no special training as anyone can almost do it. The one question that most interested individuals would like to know is whether they have to buy their own kayak or rent a kayak instead? The more ideal option between the two is the latter as there are several benefits that you can get from it such as: Number 1. Cost effective &#8211; it will cost you around 200 to 800 dollars each to buy a brand new recreational kayak while renting one might just cost you a minimal fee of 15 to 50 dollars per trip per day. Even more, the shuttling is provided often with rented kayaks. Number 2. Relieve stress &#8211; kayaking brings you closer to nature and helps you in relaxing your mind. This works as a therapy in making you calm and giving peace of mind in other words.<br />\n<a href="http://yourkayakrentalguide.postbit.com/benefits-that-come-with-renting-a-kayak.html">The Best Advice About Kayaks I&#8217;ve Ever Written</a><br />\n Number 3. Excellent workout activity &#8211; when you are kayaking, expect that it will require you lots of strength in order to paddle your way through water. In addition to that, after some time of doing this, you are more likely to have a toned body as it is great for developing your abdominal muscles.<br />\n<a href="http://paddleboardrentals.snack.ws/">What I Can Teach You About Kayaks</a><br />\n Number 4. Lose weight while having fun &#8211; it helps you in burning lots of calories in your body since kayaking requires lots of energy and strength to paddle your way through water. Without the feeling of getting tired, it is so easy to spend time in doing this activity. Of course, the more you spend time practicing, the more calories you&#8217;re able to burn. Number 5. It can be done in group or individually &#8211; this said activity can be enjoyed be it your alone or with group of friends. If you do this alone, this will surely be relaxing and peaceful and if you want it to become lively and fun, do it with group of friends. Number 6. No age limitation &#8211; this is just among the numerous activities that anyone at any stage in their lives can try. Number 7. Increases your stamina &#8211; it is helpful to increase the stamina you have if you do this on a regular basis. While practicing, it can help you to tone your body and therefore, proven to be useful for total body fitness. Say for example that this is just your first time in this said activity, then it is recommended that you understand the fundamental rules of kayaking in order to enjoy it and at the same time, rent a kayak instead of buying one to see how you perform in the waters. By doing this, you can avoid wasting forking out hundreds of cash for something you won&#8217;t be doing.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:62:"http://wp4sae.org/why-people-think-kayaks-are-a-good-idea/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:37:"Learning The “Secrets” of Options";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:49:"http://wp4sae.org/learning-the-secrets-of-options";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"http://wp4sae.org/learning-the-secrets-of-options#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 12 Apr 2016 14:40:19 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:18:"Sports & Athletics";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:49:"http://wp4sae.org/learning-the-secrets-of-options";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:422:"Tips on Buying the Right Fishing Equipment Fishing is undoubtedly one of the best ways to spend a weekend or holiday. This is something for everyone, whatever their gender or age (children need supervision, of course). In any case, this is an activity reserved for sunny afternoons, when all the day&#8217;s tasks are completed and<a class="more-link" href="http://wp4sae.org/learning-the-secrets-of-options">Read more</a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"writer";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2928:"<p><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0e/Angler_at_devizes_england_arp.jpg" style="width:317px;float:left;margin:1em" />Tips on Buying the Right Fishing Equipment Fishing is undoubtedly one of the best ways to spend a weekend or holiday. This is something for everyone, whatever their gender or age (children need supervision, of course). In any case, this is an activity reserved for sunny afternoons, when all the day&#8217;s tasks are completed and family members are free. However, to make sure that you actually enjoy the activity as you intended, you need to have the right gear. If you&#8217;ve been fishing for a while, perhaps you already know what you need. But those who are trying this pastime for the first time sure need to read some tips on how to buy fishing equipment. First and foremost, you should know the type or types of fish you&#8217;re planning to catch so you can determine what equipment is necessary. If you&#8217;re going to a pond, river or lake, find out what fish are there. That&#8217;s because different fish require different gear, from rods to lures to reels and the rest.<br />\n<a href="https://tryfishingequipmentblog.wordpress.com/2016/04/11/how-to-buy-fishing-equipment/">Smart Tips For Finding Gear</a><br />\n Price is another consideration you have to make. As with any other item you have to purchase, price is not an indication of quality. That means the most expensive gear nor the least expensive one is not necessarily the best. Find that middleground while keeping in mind that anything too cheap always comes with a catch. Buy is the best gear that fits your budget.<br />\n<a href="http://bestfishingequipment.zohosites.com/">Case Study: My Experience With Fishing</a><br />\n When buying a fishing rod, buy one that is of medium weight and at least 6 feet long, and make sure it comes with instructions. With this length, you can fish far from the boat and you will feel more comfortable doing it. Of course, it will be much easier to handle a rod of medium weight because you get a good grip of it and yet it&#8217;s not too heavy. Rods made from foam or oak are preferable. A fishing line with a weight of 4lbs and a length of 10 feet is a good choice because it can be used with a variety of fishing styles. Also, get a reel that all family members will find comfortable. The middle line rod is highly recommended because it is cheap and can also be used for many fishing styles. Finally, do get a tacklebox. This is just a box that can carry hooks, sinks and robbers. Get one that can accommodate a lot of these things, just in case you need spare. These are the most important things you need to get as you begin your new hobby of fishing. You may need many other things while you go along, but you should always start with the basics. It&#8217;s also a great idea to ask for help when buying your gear, preferably from a friend who also fishes.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:54:"http://wp4sae.org/learning-the-secrets-of-options/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:39:"What Has Changed Recently With Options?";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"http://wp4sae.org/what-has-changed-recently-with-options";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:64:"http://wp4sae.org/what-has-changed-recently-with-options#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 12 Apr 2016 14:04:29 +0000";s:7:"